  "guide": {
    "title": "Ekitabo ekikwata ku kukwata ebifaananyi mu Suno",
    "subtitle": "Engeri y'okukwatamu eddoboozi ne guitar takes that get the best results.",
    "intro": "Suno asinga kukola bulungi n’ebijuliziddwa ebiyonjo, ebitaliimu kubuusabuusa. Ekitabo kino kikwata ku kwetegeka, emitendera gy‟ebigendererwa, n‟ekiwandiiko ky‟okukwata eddakiika 3–5.",
    "sections": {
      "prep": {
        "title": "Okwetegeka",
        "body": "Wandiika mu kisenge ekirongooseddwa oba ekirimu ebintu ebigonvu bingi (kateni, rugs, engoye mu kabada). Ggyako abawagizi n'ekintu kyonna ekiwuuma. Bbugumya eddoboozi lyo okumala eddakiika 5 nga tonnakwata."
      },
      "levels": {
        "title": "Emitendera: -12 okutuuka ku -6 dBFS",
        "body": "Genderera entikko wakati wa -12 ne -6 dBFS ku mita. Wansi w’obuwanvu obwo, amaloboozi ag’emabega geeyongera okweyoleka; waggulu waakyo, akabi k’okusalako kalinnya. Kozesa mita ku lupapula lwa Record okuteekawo gain yo nga tonnatandika."
      },
      "distance": {
        "title": "Ebanga lya mic: 15–30 cm",
        "body": "Sigala sentimita 15 ku 30 okuva ku mayirofooni. Okusemberera okusinga ekyo kiyitirizanga plosives ne proximity effect; ewala akwata reverb y’ekisenge n’amaloboozi amangi."
      },
      "script": {
